#comment: The ultimate shooting range! You start with 4 sunflowers, extra 30k sun, faster sun from the sky and Gold Leaf however you are faced with one massive task - to get 32.5 million points of score. The lawn was modified so it would be harder to shoot zombies, banned all primary sun producers and Hocus Crocus, added Bassist from AltverZ to damage your defensive plants. May the bread be with you

objdata.Description:
Survive and protect the endangered plant
Survive with a special seed bank
Bonus Objective: Try not to use secondary sun producers
